I opened an issue at https://github.com/ferram4/Ferram-Aerospace-Research/issues/206

btw https://github.com/ferram4/Ferram-Aerospace-Research/issues/206#issuecomment-311803381

 

Searching the web for "clampinedInc" I only find this thread - very disappointing ...

Edited July 12, 2017 by Gordon Dry

@Gordon Dry I had a similar issue but neither FAR nor Remote Tech installed. If you're using RealPlume, you might consider updating SmokeScreen manually and going for the newest dev release of MJ in any case. I use #731 currently. It seems to have ruled out the clampinedInc spam at least in my install. Maybe that helps.

 

Cheers
